{"tid":2079689,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盧寵茂：推薦香港用中國產試劑 較為便宜！","createTime":"2020-06-26T03:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T03:47:48.000Z","uid":7542,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d643cc86d9748b97d4b6716c64aa351a8fd54359","tid":2079689,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:00:53.000Z","msg":"港大深圳醫院院長盧寵茂表示，內地製作檢測試劑成本較便宜，建議香港聯合廣東省政府聯合採購，可減低檢測成本，檢測價格相信可降至500元或以下。盧寵茂接受本台節目《千禧年代》電話訪問，他表示，如分散在不同實驗室做檢測，因檢測量不大，令成本增加，如可以集中一至兩間實驗室處理，每日做過千個檢測，實驗室有一定的檢測量，可以使用自動儀器處理，能減少人力資源和成本。他指出，<strong>經廣東省集體採購後，試劑的價格大幅下降，國產核酸檢測試劑質量無問題</strong>，港大深圳醫院亦有使用，每次檢測的價錢降至175元。但香港醫學會傳染病顧問委員會主席梁子超在同一節目指出，試劑價錢並非決定檢測成本的全部因素，需要考慮試劑的品質、實驗室適應和儀器使用等，檢測成本亦要視乎實驗室的感染控制、保護衣和檢測安排。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qrhhs9O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQrhhs9O.jpg&h=9e0aa224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534202-20200626.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534202-20200626.htm&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SlQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=10d71b8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534202-20200626.htm&h=6c31087b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534202-20200626.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔驗仲平啦，係咪？</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n=====<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>思想準備，由你做起！</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCVXu-cP74qbMuDhovt5--lg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCVXu-cP74qbMuDhovt5--lg&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SlQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=69da270c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCVXu-cP74qbMuDhovt5--lg</a>"},{"pid":"70397c705cda844